      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <ul>
          <li>Menu height adapts to content, up to full screen height</li>
          <li>Native-style scroll arrows when content overflows (no scrollbar)</li>
          <li>Single "Refresh All" button replaces per-account refresh</li>
          <li>Parallel account refresh via TaskGroup</li>
          <li>Fix: current account no longer duplicated in switch list</li>
          <li>Fix: cancelled status no longer shown in UI</li>
          <li>Fix: Sparkle gracefully handles SwiftPM debug builds</li>
        </ul>
